1.board is 15x15
2.screen size of game is 31x15
3.snake starts 3 blocks long
4.1 apple = 1 point (for every point a snake get 1 block longer)
5.when 1 of the players eats an apple then the apple
reappears in a different place on BOTH players boards
6.if a players hits a wall or himself then he loses,
regardless of how many points he has
7.first one to get to length 33 wins